(Rivergate Flood Resilience Brief) Tj
T*
(Source ID: rivergate_flood_resilience) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(This fictional city brief was created for teaching RAG retrieval and evaluation.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Rivergate is a fictional river city with low neighborhoods along the Alder River. The city) Tj
T*
(council identifies spring floods, storm surge from the lower basin, and overloaded drainage) Tj
T*
(pipes as the main climate risks. The highest exposure is in Alder Quay, Millbank, and the) Tj
T*
(Canal View senior housing area.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(The first priority is a blue-green corridor east of Millbank. The plan restores 18 hectares of) Tj
T*
(wetlands and reconnects two old side channels to slow flood water before it reaches homes.) Tj
T*
(Engineers expect the corridor to reduce peak water levels during medium floods and create) Tj
T*
(temporary storage during heavy rain.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Rivergate will also install removable flood barriers along Alder Quay. The barriers are not) Tj
T*
(permanent walls. They are stored near the quay and deployed when the river forecast crosses) Tj
T*
(the orange alert threshold. The city chose removable barriers because businesses wanted daily) Tj
T*
(access to the waterfront.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(The monitoring program adds 42 smart river gauges and rain sensors. The gauges report water) Tj
T*
(level, flow speed, and blocked drain warnings every 10 minutes. Emergency managers use this) Tj
T*
(data to decide when to close the quay road and when to open evacuation route R-3 toward North) Tj
T*
(Hill School.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(The social vulnerability section gives special attention to Canal View senior housing. During) Tj
T*
(high flood alerts, volunteers check ground-floor apartments, arrange accessible transport, and) Tj
T*
(move medicine storage to the second floor community room. The plan says that flood protection) Tj
T*
(is not successful if vulnerable residents cannot act on warnings.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Phase one has a budget of 7.8 million city credits over three years. The target is to keep the) Tj
T*
(community center, the clinic, and the main grocery store dry during a 1-in-50-year river) Tj
T*
(flood. The plan does not claim to remove all risk. It aims to reduce damage, improve warning) Tj
T*
(time, and make evacuation decisions easier.) Tj
T*
() Tj
